metadata.name: House of Birds #118
metadata.description:
"House of Birds" started as a few origami birds inside a frame.
But, birds don't need boundaries; birds need trees, hills, and sky.

Created using p5js;

Press "s" to save as png.

Twitter: @SapirCohen__

metadata.name: Latent Garden #145
metadata.description: representation of flowers in a latent space garden

metadata.name: Guise #36
metadata.description:
Abstract animated structures evolve and spread endlessly. Inspired by pattern repetitions found in nature. 

Created with GLSL and p5.js. Best viewed in fullscreen.

metadata.name: Forced Ink #25
metadata.description:
Forced Ink is an experiment in using physical forces (repulsion) to create digital artwork reminiscent of a real-world abstract painting.

Features
Color: a random color
Particle Count: between 100 and 450, equal chance
Particle Size: between 5 and 15, equal chance

metadata.description:
Welcome to the Lazy Kitties Society!

Be the guardian of these cute kitties born in the Tezos blockchain space.
And please be a part of our Lazy Kitties Society!
https://discord.gg/lazykitties

Let's create a wonderful world with kittens! MEOW!

[Mouse Movement]: Eye Control
[Press 'c' or 'C'] : Kitten's Favorite Cushion (Toggle)
[Press 's' or 'S'] : Save Snapshot (With BG)
[Press 't' or 'T'] : Save Snapshot (Transparent BG)
